These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
There are 7 different favourite colors: grey, lavender, azure, blood-red, pink, mauve, brown
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, old-henry, aristoff, tiparillo, bongani, vegafina
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes grey##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the vegafina-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is between the aristoff-smoker and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person who likes azure##1
11. the person who likes mauve is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the montecristo-smoker is the person who likes pink##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the old-henry-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Color   | grey  | blood-red        | lavender  | brown     | mauve   | azure       | pink   |
| Cigar         | blend   | vegafina | aristoff    | old-henry  | tiparillo | bongani | montecristo |

