.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, horror, adventure, action, western, disaster, scientific
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, blend, pall-mall, dunhill, game, vegafina
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is between the person who's sport is soccer and the vegafina-smoker##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
12. the montecristo-smoker is the person watching horror movies##1
13. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is on the right of the game-smoker##1
15. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | scientific      | action     | spy  | western | adventure | horror |
| Sport         | cricket  | badminton | snowboarding | handball | soccer | parkour   | sailing  |
| Cigar     | blend   | game     | vegafina        | pall-mall  | dunhill   | ritmeester       | montecristo      |

