.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk, tea, water
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, brazilian, indonesian, nigerian, chinese, mexican, indian
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, december, june, september, february, may, november
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is the canadian##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is the nigerian##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the chinese##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in november and the indian##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
10. the indonesian is on the right of the mexican##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is the canadian##1
12. the indonesian is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the nigerian##1
14. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking water##1
15. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | coffee     | soy-milk   | tea        | fanta   | iced-tea     | milk     | water    |
