.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: apricot, banana, blueberry, cranberry, pumpkin, radish, strawberry
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, poker, whist, scrabble, domino, chess
There are 7 different favourite colors: red, apricot, light-blue, ivory, white, black, lilac
 1. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing domino is the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is the person playing whist##1
 4. the person playing go is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes red is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person who likes black is the person playing mah-jongg##1
10. the person who likes red is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person playing poker is the person who likes lilac##1
12. the person eating banana is the person who likes white##1
13. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
14. the person playing chess is between the person playing poker and the person playing whist##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Food          | banana  | radish    | pumpkin  | apricot | cranberry  | strawberry | blueberry |
| Game   | scrabble | poker | chess   | whist   | domino | mah-jongg     | go |
| Color   | white | lilac   | red | light-blue  | apricot   | black    | ivory    |

